## rules-mirror
.TP
\f[B]sovereign-osctl rules-mirror [arguments]\f[R]
M060 D-12 (MS024 + MS038 + MS039): READ-ONLY consumer of the selfdef
nftables rules mirror (MS007 typed-mirror crate selfdef-rules-mirror).
Projects the daemon\[cq]s Ring 0..4 nftables rule projection for the
D-12 networking dashboards (edge-firewall + network-edge).
Rule installation lives in selfdefctl + nft at the IPS layer (operator
